sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Email as Resend Email

    User->>Browser: Navigate to Orgs → "Create Organization" tab
    Browser->>Browser: Enter organization name and description
    User->>Browser: Click "Submit Request"
    Browser->>API: POST /api/organizations
    Note right of Browser: Body: { name, description }
    API->>DB: Validate: no existing pending request for this user
    API->>DB: OrgRequest.create(name, desc, requesterId, status: PENDING)
    DB-->>API: New org request
    API->>Email: sendOrgRequestSubmittedEmail(user)
    Email-->>User: "Your request has been submitted"
    API-->>Browser: 201 Created
